[[iftags +样版]]
++ 很好奇这是什么？去看[https://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/style-guide 图书馆格式指导]吧！[[footnote]]**译注：**或者懒得去看版：
@@[[include :scp-wiki-cn:wanderers:component:navbar @@
@@|left=[/页面名称 上一篇的文本]（也可以只写文本不写链接）@@
@@|center=中心页/系列页文本（也可以写链接）@@
@@|right=[/页面名称 下一篇的文本]（也可以只写文本不写链接）@@
@@]]@@[[/footnote]]
[[/iftags]]
[[module CSS]]
:root {
    --navbar-base-font-size: .8em;
/* ===STANDARD THEME COLORS=== */
    --navbar-gray-monochrome: 45, 70, 45;
    /* green */
    --navbar-dark-gray-monochrome: 30, 55, 30;
    /* dark green gray for sidebar background */
    --navbar-black-monochrome: 12, 12, 12;
    /* black */
    --navbar-bright-accent: 255, 219, 90;
    /* bright yellow */
    --navbar-medium-accent: 228, 180, 28;
    /* medium yellow */
    --navbar-dark-accent: var(--navbar-dark-gray-monochrome);
    /* dark yellow */
}

/* Navbar */

.footer-wikiwalk-nav {
    font-size: 90%;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.wlnavbar {
    --navbar-text-shadow: rgba(var(--navbar-black-monochrome), 0.35);
    --navbar-box-shadow: rgb(var(--navbar-gray-monochrome));
    --navbar-border-color: rgb(var(--navbar-medium-accent));
    margin: 0.625rem 0 0.938rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.250rem;
    padding: 0.125rem;
    border: outset 0.188rem var(--navbar-border-color);
    border-radius: 0.0625rem;
    background-color: rgb(var(--navbar-dark-gray-monochrome));
    box-shadow: 0.09375rem 0.09375rem 0.188rem var(--navbar-box-shadow);
    color: rgb(var(--navbar-medium-accent));
    text-shadow: 0.0625rem 0.0625rem 0.125rem var(--navbar-text-shadow);
}

.wlnavbar a {
    display: inline-block;
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    padding-top: 0.45em;
    padding-bottom: 0.35em;
    color: rgb(var(--navbar-bright-accent));
}

.wlnavbar a::before {
    display: flex;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100%;
    font-size: calc(var(--navbar-base-font-size) * 1.1);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: calc(var(--navbar-base-font-size) * 0.8);
}

.wlnavbar .footer-wikiwalk-nav {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 90%;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.025em;
}

.wlnavbar .footer-wikiwalk-nav * {
    line-height: 1em;
}

.wlnavbar .footer-wikiwalk-nav .center {
    flex-basis: content;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.3rem;
    text-align: center;
}

.wlnavbar .footer-wikiwalk-nav .left,
.wlnavbar .footer-wikiwalk-nav .right {
    display: inline-flex;
    position: relative;
    flex-basis: calc(40% - 3em);
    align-items: center;
    font-size: calc(var(--navbar-base-font-size) * 0.8);
}

.wlnavbar .footer-wikiwalk-nav .left {
    justify-content: flex-end;
    margin: 0.35em 0 0.35em 0.35em;
    padding-right: 0.5em;
    padding-left: 1em;
    border-right: 0.0625rem solid rgb(var(--navbar-dark-accent));
    text-align: right;
}

.wlnavbar .left > a::before {
    content: "↫";
    left: -0.75em;
    transition: left 1s ease-in-out;
    will-change: left;
    -webkit-animation: bounce-left 1.7s infinite;
     animation: bounce-left 1.7s infinite;
    -webkit-animation-play-state: paused;
     animation-play-state: paused;
}

.wlnavbar .left > a:hover::before {
    -webkit-animation-play-state: running;
     animation-play-state: running;
}

.wlnavbar .footer-wikiwalk-nav .right {
    justify-content: flex-start;
    margin: 0.35em 0.35em 0.35em 0;
    padding-right: 1em;
    padding-left: 0.5em;
    border-left: 0.0625rem solid rgb(var(--navbar-dark-accent));
    text-align: left;
}

.wlnavbar .right > a::before {
    content: "↬";
    right: -0.75em;
    transition: right 1s ease-in-out;
    will-change: right;
    -webkit-animation: bounce-right 1.7s infinite;
     animation: bounce-right 1.7s infinite;
    -webkit-animation-play-state: paused;
     animation-play-state: paused;
}

.wlnavbar .right > a:hover::before {
    -webkit-animation-play-state: running;
     animation-play-state: running;
}
[[/module]]

[[div class="wlnavbar"]]
[[div class="footer-wikiwalk-nav"]]
[[div_ class="left"]]
{$left}
[[/div]]
[[div_ class="center"]]
[[size 120%]]{$center}[[/size]]
[[/div]]
[[div_ class="right"]]
{$right}
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
